Package io.ataraxic.nomicflux.voyageur

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Context<A,N extends Node<A>,E extends Edge<A,N,E>,I extends Iterable<E>>
    A context surrounding a Node and it's outgoing and ingoing Edges
    Edge<A,N extends Node<A>,E extends Edge<A,N,E>>
    An edge from one Node to another
    Graph<A,N extends Node<A>,E extends Edge<A,N,E>,I extends Iterable<E>,G extends Graph<A,N,E,I,G>>
    Main interface for working with inductive graphs
    LabeledNode<A,L>
    A Node which also carries a label containing node metadata
    Node<A>
    A Node containing a value, which serves as its (presumed unique) ID
    WeightedEdge<A,N extends Node<A>,W,E extends WeightedEdge<A,N,W,E>>
    An Edge with additional weight metadata
